==English==
===Noun===
'''muzzle'''
#[[mouth]] a dog etc.
#open end of a gun etc. that the bullet emerges from as opposed to the [[breech]]
#a device used to stop a dog etc. from biting

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[kuono]], [[turpa]]

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|muzzl|e|}}
#to apply a muzzle
#to restrain (from speaking or acting), to reign in

====Translations====
